Hey, Ran!

372
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:10,180
What's wrong?

373
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:11,380
Ran!

374
00:24:11,380 --> 00:24:13,980
I remember that something like this happened before.

375
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:19,880
When there were a series of high school girls being hit-and-run...

